       of  creating either binary or ASCII output with _v_._i_n_._d_x_f.  Since _v_._c_a_d_-
       _l_a_b_e_l works only  on  binary  vector  files,  the  ASCII  GRASS  vector
       (dig_ascii)  files  that are generated by _v_._i_n_._d_x_f must be converted to
       binary GRASS vector (dig) files using  the  _v_._i_n_._a_s_c_i_i  program  before
