       _v_._c_a_d_l_a_b_e_l searches a binary GRASS vector file of contour lines to find
       the contour lines that are closest to each box (contour label)  in  the
       binary  GRASS  vector  file containing contour labels.  The two contour
       lines that are closest to a box are tagged with the same label (an ele-
       vation value) as that of the box.

